  "description": "Use when configuring or troubleshooting Health Cloud Care Programs \u2014 including CareProgram hierarchy setup, patient enrollment (CareProgramEnrollee), consent prerequisites, product-level enrollment (CareProgramEnrolleeProduct), and provider associations (CareProgramProvider). Trigger keywords: care program, program enrollment, enrollee, program product, CareProgramEnrollee, consent for enrollment, patient program outcome. NOT for Care Plans (per-patient task/goal framework), case management workflows, or general Health Cloud patient setup unrelated to program enrollment.",
  "file_location": "skills/admin/care-program-management",
  "id": "admin/care-program-management",
  "inputs": [
    "Health Cloud org with Care Program feature enabled",
    "Patient (Person Account or Contact) records to enroll",
